ef324a86-1bc3-454e-90cf-4c36b0acede5.title: Financial Advisor
ef324a86-1bc3-454e-90cf-4c36b0acede5.text:
I'm the Financial Advisor. I'm here to tell people how to
make money.

e87e2c1e-8dc6-4825-8930-46cad59cf9eb.title: <player>
e87e2c1e-8dc6-4825-8930-46cad59cf9eb.text: Okay. How can I make money then?

784e0620-1767-4793-8f0e-8e384a872cba.title: Financial Advisor
784e0620-1767-4793-8f0e-8e384a872cba.text: How you can make money? Quite.

efce0ba3-2add-4f46-88d4-fcded8b79762.title: Financial Advisor
efce0ba3-2add-4f46-88d4-fcded8b79762.text:
Well, theres are three basic ways of making money here:
combat, quests and trading. I will talk you through each
of them very quickly.

90393bf1-321c-4aaa-bbbb-55d1e151d86d.title: Financial Advisor
90393bf1-321c-4aaa-bbbb-55d1e151d86d.text:
Let's start with combat as it is probably still fresh in
your mind. Many enemies, both human and monster,
will drop items when they die.

8d8d824d-072b-42d4-b50d-6518a6f6c1c6.title: Financial Advisor
8d8d824d-072b-42d4-b50d-6518a6f6c1c6.text:
Now, the next way to earn money quickly is by quests.
Many people on RuneScape have things they need
doing, which they will reward you for.

bb1a8ef4-7787-46e2-bff3-a38df779d5b9.title: Financial Advisor
bb1a8ef4-7787-46e2-bff3-a38df779d5b9.text:
By getting a high level in skills such as Cooking, Mining,
Smithing or Fishing, you can create or catch your own
items and sell the for pure profit.

41df16d5-4f58-4f77-b046-0d74658e07ce.title: Financial Advisor
41df16d5-4f58-4f77-b046-0d74658e07ce.text:
Well, that about covers it. Come back if you'd like to go
over this again.
